    <span>B. Find the words from the text that mean the following.</span>
    <br>
    <br>
    a. misleading or illusionary (<b>deceptive</b>)
    <br>
    <br>
    b. in a natural state; not yet processed or refined (<b>crude</b>)
    <br>
    <br>
    c. a mystical horse like animal with a single straight horn projecting from its forehead
    (<b>unicorn</b>)
    <br>
    <br>
    d. never dying or decaying (<b>immortal</b>)
    <br>
    <br>
    e. come to an end; stop (<b>cease</b>)
    <br>
    <br>
    f. to activate or put into motion (<b>actuate</b>)
